Invocation Name: cricket world cup winner
des:
This skill lists out winners of different Cricket World Cups which have been organised over the years right from 1975 to 2015. This skill also tells about the runner-up teams and the margin of the victory. In addition, it also tells about the number of times a particular team has won the world cup.

 Note: All the data is related to Men's Cricket World Cup curated and organised by the International Cricket Council.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
